   456→   *   <li>Extracts description, label, and range classes</li>
   457→   *   <li>Creates an ObjectPropertyMapper to generate the schema</li>
   458→   *   <li>Adds the property to the resource schema</li>
   459→   *   <li>Marks as required if restrictions indicate requiredness</li>
   460→   * </ol>
